    "description": "Welcome to Realm's Crossing, where the classic thrill of strategy board games converges with modern technology to allow advanced mechanics and stunning visuals. Prepare to engage in epic battles, strategic alliances, and tactical manoeuvres to snatch the victory under your opponents noses.<br><br>Balance between marching your armies, expanding your empire by building and recruiting new units to support your Conquest. Don't forget to secure resource supply lines to maintain your Empire!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/051982f615fe656a5edd2bbe2e0b2093.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/051982f615fe656a5edd2bbe2e0b2093.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/051982f615fe656a5edd2bbe2e0b2093.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2>Play with up to 5 players, either locally or remote. You can also replace any number of players with computer AI. Whether you’re playing solo or with friends, the game adapts to your needs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/7019a52a1e160e847e813a841615e899.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/7019a52a1e160e847e813a841615e899.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/7019a52a1e160e847e813a841615e899.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Win Conditions</h2>There are many ways to achieve Victory. Other than Military Conquest, building, trading and resource control are viable ways to win the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/3eaab436588b14ad4da3ddf367f37c6a.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/3eaab436588b14ad4da3ddf367f37c6a.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/3eaab436588b14ad4da3ddf367f37c6a.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Playable Races</h2>There are five playable races, Undead, Elves, Orcs, Giants and Humans. Each having unique perks and heroes. Find the one that best suits your playstyle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/d853e8da9493ca6f71b25aea5bb8f9de.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/d853e8da9493ca6f71b25aea5bb8f9de.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/d853e8da9493ca6f71b25aea5bb8f9de.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Heroes</h2>Each race has their own hero with their unique magical power and strengths and weaknesses. Some are great at supporting their armies while others perform well on their own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/2a11f07813194f477bb26de94e7b61a5.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/2a11f07813194f477bb26de94e7b61a5.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/2a11f07813194f477bb26de94e7b61a5.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Movements</h2>Create an effective army that suits your need. Footmen are cost efficient but slow, Cavalry is fast but expensive and Archers are great at supporting but require protection.<br><br>Keep your units alive so they can level up and get stronger!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/0c9f058ee87b14d4358268065a0baad7.poster.avif?t=1734444190\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/0c9f058ee87b14d4358268065a0baad7.webm?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3148940/extras/0c9f058ee87b14d4358268065a0baad7.mp4?t=1734444190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Turn Based Gameplay</h2>Play in your own time without stress. Take a break if you have to and pick up the game whenever you wish to continue.",
